title: C9C - Music For Robot Dance Parties 2016 WAV
description:
13 tracks of deadly industrial dance tunes, ideal for robot raves! Hear the sounds of the 1980s transposed to the Planet of the Info-Bots!

Special Thanks to the staff at Star Worlds Arcade for letting us record in their retro gaming room and consult some of the greatest video arcade machine designers, programmers, artists, players and pinball wizards ever assembled!
www.starworldsarcade.com

No robots or video arcade machines were harmed during this recording.
credits
released February 3, 2016

Pat Thomas (keyboard/mixing)
Ken Gage (keyboard/mixing)
Mike Schusler (all guitars, except Track 14)
Michael T. Daffenberg (guitar on Track 14)
